Purpose:

This utility allows the user to upload files to Amazon Glacier via python 
2.7 via boto.

Usage: 

usage: glacierUpload.py [-h] [--vault VAULT] [--key KEY] [--secret SECRET]
                        [--file FILE] [--description DESC]

  -h, --help          show this help message and exit
  --vault VAULT       AWS Glacier Vault (if it doesn't exist, we will create
                      it.)
  --key KEY           AWS API Key Id (aws_awsKeyId)
  --secret SECRET     AWS secret (aws_secret_access_key)
  --file FILE         Path and filename (upload source)
  --description DESC  Optional description.